    {
      "@id": "blk:md:knowgrph-ontology-document:list:26:1",
      "@type": "List",
      "labels": [
        "List"
      ],
      "name": "List 1",
      "chunk_text": "**Multi-Ontology Dataset**: `docs/assets/multi-ontology-kg.jsonld` implements domain-agnostic assessment graphs combining PROV-O, MEX, P-Plan, ML Schema, GeoSPARQL, and RO-Crate.\n**Schema-Config Templates**: `schema-config/knowgrph-schema-config-template.jsonld` transforms ontology terms into styled graph nodes via type selectors and layer configuration; `schema-config/knowgrph-interviewer-schema-config.jsonld` coordinates multi-ontology styling with semantic layer defaults.\n**Canvas Pipeline Integration**: `canvas/src/features/parsers/examplesCatalog.ts` and `canvas/src/features/parsers/workflowPresets.ts` expose preset-driven dataset loading and rendering.",
      "properties": {
        "order": 1
      },
      "metadata": {
        "parsedAt": "2026-05-24T02:20:52+00:00",
        "source": "knowgrph_parser.graph_builder",
        "codebaseRoot": "/Users/huijoohwee/Documents/GitHub/knowgrph",
        "codebaseRelPath": "docs/documents/knowgrph-ontology-document.md",
